{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"GamepadEvent","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GamepadEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API\">Gamepad API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GamepadEvent\"><code>GamepadEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>构造函数</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GamepadEvent/GamepadEvent\"><code>GamepadEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GamepadEvent/gamepad\"><code>gamepad</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Gamepad API 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Gamepad\"><code>Gamepad</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GamepadButton\"><code>GamepadButton</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getGamepads\"><code>Navigator.getGamepads()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Gamepad API 的 GamepadEvent 接口包含对连接到系统的控制器的引用，这也是 gamepad 事件 events <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>Window.gamepadconnected</code></a> 与 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>Window.gamepaddisconnected</code></a> 被触发时响应的内容。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"构造函数","title":"构造函数","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"gamepadevent\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GamepadEvent/GamepadEvent\" title=\"GamepadEvent()\"><code>GamepadEvent()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>返回一个新的 <code>GamepadEvent</code> 对象。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"gamepadevent.gamepad\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GamepadEvent/gamepad\"><code>GamepadEvent.gamepad</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>返回一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Gamepad\"><code>Gamepad</code></a> 对象，提供触发事件的控制器数据的访问。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>在触发的 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>Window.gamepadconnected</code></a> 事件上调用控制器属性。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"gamepadconnected\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"控制器已连接于 %d 位：%s。 %d 个按键，%d 个坐标方向。\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>gamepad<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>index<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>gamepad<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>gamepad<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>buttons<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>gamepad<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>axes<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>与 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>Window.gamepaddisconnected</code></a> 事件上的。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"gamepaddisconnected\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"控制器已从 %d 位断开：%s\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>gamepad<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>index<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>gamepad<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/gamepad/#gamepadevent-interface","title":"Gamepad"}],"query":"api.GamepadEvent"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.GamepadEvent","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GamepadEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另请参阅","title":"另请参阅","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/en-US/doc